&lt;p&gt;Large size partition metadata is causing this issue&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;eg., impala stores huge stats chunk in partitionMetadata with &lt;b&gt;param_keys = (impala_intermediate_stats_chunk&lt;/b&gt;{*}), these PARTITION_PARAM_KEYS are not required for Hive. These params should be skipped while preparing partition object from HMS to HS2.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Similar to &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HIVE-25501&quot; title=&quot;Provide a configurable filter for removing useless properties from PartitionDesc objects before MapWork serialization&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;HIVE-25501&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;HIVE-25501&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, any user defined regex param_keys should be skipped in listPartitions HMS API call response.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
