                            <comment id="17782814" author="dengzh" created="Sat, 4 Nov 2023 03:06:53 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Fix has been pushed to master. Thank you &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=hemanth619&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;hemanth619&quot;&gt;hemanth619&lt;/a&gt; for the review!&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The property filter introduced in &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HIVE-20306&quot; title=&quot;Implement projection spec for fetching only requested fields from partitions&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;HIVE-20306&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;HIVE-20306&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; behaves like the standard SQL pattern matching, please use &lt;tt&gt;_&lt;/tt&gt;&#160;to match any single character and&#160;&lt;tt&gt;%&lt;/tt&gt; to match an arbitrary number of characters. If the filter has some special chars escape, it may work as not expected on JDO path, for example: %impala\\\_.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
